OOC:  Hey you guys.  Since Yanshosh left, I guess I should go to, 
but i won't i am now going to fulfill my psoting responsibilitis.  
Since Kinger comes and goes,  I will take control of the Destrons 
and take Neody, if anyone objects email me privatly.

To many more years of NBWRPG.


BIC:

Halucigen walked around his new desk in his control office.  It was 
stuggle to get here from Alliance Island and finally take control of 
the Destrons.  

---------------------

Inside the D.E.D ship a call came in from Cybertron.  "You have 
been ordered back to cybertron.
The ship began to lift off with a little time for some bots to escape if 
they wanted to stay.
---------
Firestrike walked into the Decepticon base as he headed to talk to 
Megatron.

------
Grounded walked into the conference room, waiting to see who 
was in there.
